attributes.title: worst app ever 💅🏻
attributes.review: i downloaded this app to support our great president donald trump. i thought he was a man with great intentions for this country, but clearly i was wrong. when i first downloaded the app, it took WEEKS to fully download so that was already a bad start. but, as soon as i opened the app my phone starts glitching with trumps nudes playing a song called Gangnam Style “Hey Sexy Lady” and i was completely traumatized by that. ✨then all of a sudden, my cat does a triple back flip off the ceiling and jumps out the window! i was truly and utterly terrified. 😖 so i went to go look for my cat around my neighborhood, and i see a crackhead running at me bare naked with a sun hat on, holding a pocket knife with a trump 2020 sign yelling “he’s going to get you!” so i ran the opposite direction!! 🏃🏼‍♀️then i found a frog molesting my cat behind the bushes next me! 🙈i take my cat and i run back to my house and i come inside to see my uncle dressed in a cow costume with his face painted orange twerking on the wall and his eyes were black!! he was screaming “possessed by trump! help me! trump got me! there’s no way out!” 👽👻 and then suddenly he disappeared. i looked through my kitchen cabinets to find holy water and salt and that’s when trumps deformed head rolled out of my cabinet and started chasing me! i had gotten a machete and chucked it at his head. and boom! it was gone! i was so shocked in disbelief of what had just happened 😰until donkey from the movie shrek appears and tells me and my cat to get on his back. so we got on and then he started flying! 🦅we flew to the white house and donkey, my cat and i kicked trumps ass. 🍊and that’s when i kicked trump in his pepe hole and he flies 8,712 miles and lands in the pacific ocean and gets eaten by the megladon shark. 🦈then donkey vanishes into thin air 💨and my cat and i took a flight back home and everything was okay. ✅ truly the craziest experience i’ve ever gone through!! i am currently taking therapy and i will continue to do so for next 15 years. what a traumatic experience! 😪 do NOT download this app! 💅🏻
